snippet.title: Aerofly FS 4 Flight Simulator - Official Trailer for Windows, Mac and Linux
snippet.description:
Now available on Steam for Windows, Mac and Linux!
https://www.aerofly.com/

The Aircraft Add-On DLC includes new aircraft such as the A380, 787 Dreamliner, 747 and CRJ-900 airliners. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1oImqkjAib4
